g $99 a month to test users of Starlink, the aerospace company\'s new satellite-internet service, plus a $499 starter kit.  SpaceX is likely paying much less to manufacture Starlink terminals, but two telecommunications experts believe the company is heavily subsidizing the cost for users, and eating $1,000 to $2,000 (or more) on each. Key to making Starlink work is the starter kit\'s satellite dish, or user terminal, which Musk has nicknamed the \\"UFO on a stick.\\"", "score": 0.6747586, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://finviz.com/news/230931/spacex-changed-the-economics-of-spaceflight-now-its-doing-the-same-thing-to-satellite-cost", "title": "SpaceX Changed the Economics of Spaceflight. Now It\'s Doing the Same Thing to Satellite Cost.", "content": "internet capacity in orbit than any given ViaSat-3 launch. The math here is simple: For the same $150 million Viasat pays to launch a single ViaSat-3 with 1 Tbps of capacity, SpaceX will be able to launch 900 Starlinks, providing 900 Tbps of internet capacity. Instead of the $800 million (or even just $700 million) cost to pay Boeing to build it a ViaSat-3, SpaceX says its own construction cost for each V3 Starlink will be just $1.2 million. Oh, and instead of Viasat needing to wait years for", "score": 0.6538572, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://futurism.com/the-byte/spacex-starlink-satellite-internet-99-per-month", "title": "SpaceX\'s Starlink Satellite Internet Costs $99 Per Month | Futurism", "content": "More on Starlink: SpaceX Will Build Starlink-Like Constellation Around Mars, Its President Says", "score": 0.59796065, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.quora.com/How-do-you-calculate-the-cost-per-bit-using-satellite-and-terrestrial-networks", "title": "How to calculate the cost per bit using satellite and terrestrial networks - Quora", "content": "the cost of the satellite itself. Additionally, it will cost between $80 million and $110 million to launch the satellite into its orbit. The low side is something like a Starlink satellite that is claimed to only cost $1.5 million each. How much will SpaceX\'s satellite internet cost? Question:\\u201dHow much will SpaceX\\u2019s satellite Internet cost? A typical weather satellite costs about 290 million dollars. Question:\\u201dHow much will SpaceX\\u2019s satellite Internet cost? A typical weather satellite costs", "score": 0.55478466, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.quora.com/How-many-square-kilometers-of-signal-coverage-per-one-Starlink-satellite", "title": "How many square kilometers of signal coverage per one Starlink satellite?", "content": "satellite support at once? How many Starlink satellites are in the sky? How much does a single SpaceX Starlink satellite cost? How many users (connections) per satellite will SpaceX\'s Starlink support and will they have enough coverage per satellite to justify the cost? How many users (connections) per satellite will SpaceX\'s Starlink support and will they have enough coverage per satellite to justify the cost? The Starlink constellation is starting out with 12000+ satellites. Starlink:", "score": 0.23118909, "raw_content": null}]',
